<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idbded7569-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/89/272/s11010">section 11010 of Pub. L. 89–272</ref> was renumbered section 11009 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s6992i">section 6992i of this title</ref>.</p>
